              "content": "This framework was built to solve the challenge of creating **maintainable, scalable portfolio websites** without relying on heavy frontend frameworks or complex build systems.\n\nThe core philosophy is {{highlight}}configuration over code{{/highlight}} - content changes happen through JSON files, not code modifications. This makes it easy to add new pages, components, and profiles without touching the underlying system.\n\nKey design principles:\n- Dictionary-driven rendering for consistent data flow\n- Component isolation for maximum reusability\n- Security-first approach with protected content support\n- Theme variables for consistent styling across all components"
