              "title": "Component Loader Pattern",
              "language": "php",
              "code": "<?php\nclass ComponentLoaderT1 {\n    public function load($id, $title, $navConfig, $loadingMode, $metadata) {\n        $data = $metadata['componentData'] ?? [];\n        \n        switch ($loadingMode) {\n            case 'shell':\n                return $this->generateShell($id, $navConfig, $metadata);\n            case 'content':\n                return $this->generateContent($data);\n            case 'full':\n            default:\n                return $this->generateFullComponent($id, $navConfig, $data);\n        }\n    }\n}",
              "description": "Every component follows this three-mode loading pattern: shell for dynamic placeholders, content for API responses, and full for initial page load."
